cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with the task of 3D car instance understanding for autonomous driving, which is a computer vision problem related to robotics and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of deep convolutional neural networks, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The dataset and algorithms are specifically designed for autonomous driving, which falls under the category of cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses the use of semantic keypoints, which is related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with image processing and analysis, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia).
